title: Setgraph
description: Setgraph revolutionizes the way you plan, log, and track your workouts, ensuring you’re always progressing with precision. Whether you’re following a personalized strength training plan, logging every lift, or tracking personal records, Setgraph adapts to your needs. Designed for lifters of all levels, it prioritizes speed, precision, and customization, making planning and tracking effortless—so you can stay focused on your training.
